join nym center
do Global.mod_can_move(false)
nym: Hello, void.
nym: I am Nym, nothing but a resident living in this dreary place...
nym: All we've ever been told is...
nym: "Erase the void"
nym: "Reject the void"
nym: "Destroy the void"
nym: ...and everyone has followed out of fear.
nym: Yet I'm beginning to question whether it's worth all the effort...
do Global.mod_can_move(true)